cast.original_title: Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom
cast.overview: After arriving in India, Indiana Jones is asked by a desperate village to find a mystical stone. He agrees – and stumbles upon a secret cult plotting a terrible plan in the catacombs of an ancient palace.
cast.title: Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom

details.biography:
Sarah-Jane Hassell is an actress.

She acted in Leslie Bricusse's musical, "Doctor Doolittle," at the Apollo Victoria Theatre in London, England with Phillip Schofield, Bryan Smith, Peter Cellier, Peter Gallagher, John Rawnsley and Julie Andrews (Voice of Polynesia) in the cast. Steven Pimlott was director.
details.name: Sarah-Jane Hassell
